Check SOMA balance for an address

Usage: soma balance [OPTIONS] [ADDRESS]

Arguments:
  [ADDRESS]  Address to check (defaults to active address)

Options:
      --with-coins  Show individual coin details
      --json        Output as JSON
  -h, --help        Print help

EXAMPLES:
    soma balance
    soma balance 0x1234...5678
    soma balance --with-coins
